column5: Just got done doing some jigging in Iowa City by the power plant dam . Was using a Sirmanski Glitter Jig and landed a nice 4 lb. walleye!

You survived the wind?! I have always wanted to go try down there but never have. Normally try below the dam in Central City or Anamosa. I need to go down there someday and figure out where that area is. I always hear of people catching eyes there.
I, also, have wanted to try it, but haven't. Where do you park? Bill
